ISLAMABAD, May 13 (APP):Foreign Minister Shah Mahmood Qureshi will participate in a virtual meeting of Shanghai Cooperation Organization Council of Foreign Ministers (SCO-CFM) today which will primarily focus on COVID-19 pandemic.
The video conference will provide an opportunity to express solidarity and develop a united response to the COVID-19 pandemic at the SCO level , a Foreign Office statement said issued here.
